docs.snippet: Interest in the exhibits at the Importers' Automobile Salon centres largely in the bodies, particularly those of the enclosed type, which are mounted on the various classes because these represent the best and the latest in the coach builders' art....
docs.lead_paragraph: Interest in the exhibits at the Importers' Automobile Salon centres largely in the bodies, particularly those of the enclosed type, which are mounted on the various classes because these represent the best and the latest in the coach builders' art. This interest will be more marked than ever at this season's Salon, because several new types and radical changes in former types will make their debut.

headline.main: NEW DESIGNS FOR IMPORTERS' SALON; Highest Art of European and American Body Builders to Be Exhibited.

docs.lead_paragraph: Yesterday's dispatch from Paris relating to the revolution in Paraguay and the warning given by both Argentina and Brazil that they would not permit the bombardment of the capital city, Asuncion, was used as a text for an interview, given to a TIMES reporter by a New York lawyer who has just returned from a five-months' stay in Paraguay and Uruguay.
docs.abstract: unnamed New Yorker, on return from Paraguay, gives eyewitness acct of revolution and pol situation

headline.main: SAVAGE WAR WAGING AMONG PARAGUAYANS; New Yorker, Returning from There, Says Wounded Are All Butchered After Battles.
